* ngspice init file for PEX simulation
* Load OSDI plugins for PSP/r3_cmc/mosvar compact models
* Paths are relative to sim/ (ngspice CWD for make pex-sim)

osdi '../IHP-Open-PDK/ihp-sg13g2/libs.tech/ngspice/osdi/psp103.osdi'
osdi '../IHP-Open-PDK/ihp-sg13g2/libs.tech/ngspice/osdi/psp103_nqs.osdi'
osdi '../IHP-Open-PDK/ihp-sg13g2/libs.tech/ngspice/osdi/r3_cmc.osdi'
osdi '../IHP-Open-PDK/ihp-sg13g2/libs.tech/ngspice/osdi/mosvar.osdi'
